snippet.title: SM64 Splitscreen Multiplayer Release Trailer
snippet.description:
It's out finally! Check Gameplay here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=t8hGu-fDwsM
For more fangames, subscribe!: https://www.youtube.com/c/KazeEmanuar?sub_confirmation=1
Demos, funding: https://www.patreon.com/Kazestuff
I do livestreams!: https://www.twitch.tv/kazesm64

Download patch here: https://mega.nz/#!vbxQyaYI!EyF77s2urK-rLAaOg_edTen9H63lg_NOzpKpAs128ZA
Patcher (works in all browsers!!): https://hack64.net/tools/patcher.php
Project  64: https://www.pj64-emu.com/

Q: My screen is flickering!
A: Go into your settings and change the graphics plugin. Most of them should work.


Credit to Snowxanya for the new peach voice acting! Now luigi gets some love too:
https://www.youtube.com/user/TheSnowDroplette

Shoutouts to all the people that helped betatest this mod. This would be a very buggy release without them. Also a shoutout to cjess for providing the luigi model and Nikki and melonspeedruns for providing some texture work.
